{"data": [{"id": "4742320", "title": "Tesco Shares Are Worth Adding To Your Basket", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tesco Supermarket Shopfront\" data-id=\"458531819\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4288px\" height=\"2848px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">georgeclerk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Tesco (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSCDF\" title=\"Tesco PLC\">OTCPK:TSCDF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSCDY\" title=\"Tesco PLC\">OTCPK:TSCDY</a>) have been on a rampant run this year. Up more than 25%, the stock has not only outperformed its home benchmark in the FTSE 100 Index (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UKX\" title=\"FTSE 100 Index\">UKX</a>) but, more impressively, is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458531819/image_458531819.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742320-tesco-shares-are-worth-adding-to-your-basket", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:45:58"}, {"id": "4742311", "title": "Oxford Square Capital: Staying Far Away From This Deteriorating BDC As A Dividend Cut Is Incoming", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2141988223/image_2141988223.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Emergency savings concept\" data-id=\"2141988223\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4714066-oxford-square-capital-q2-earnings-show-little-portfolio-improvement\">previously covered</a> Oxford Square Capital (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OXSQ\" title=\"Oxford Square Capital Corp.\">OXSQ</a></span>) a quarter ago and issued a sell rating due to the poor portfolio performance since inception and the high non-accrual rate. OXSQ operates as a business development company that</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742311-oxford-square-capital-corp-staying-far-away-from-this-deteriorating-bdc-as-a-dividend-cut-is-incoming", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:41:00"}, {"id": "4742310", "title": "VICI Properties Is A Strong Buy Despite Rising Interest Rates", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1924436399/image_1924436399.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close Up Shot On Hand Of Anonymous Poker Player Checking Playing Cards He Was Dealt. Professional High S