2-05 16:35:45"}, {"id": "4742308", "title": "Daktronics Q2: Digital Transformation Set To Drive Strong Margin Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Football scoreboard with no numbers on it in the dark\" data-id=\"183305131\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1130px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Caliphoto/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment thesis</h2> <p>Shares of Daktronics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DAKT\" title=\"Daktronics, Inc.\">DAKT</a></span>) are up more than 30% since my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703453-daktronics-stock-compelling-valuation-steady-growth-improving-margins\">initial recommendation</a> in July, where I recognized the company's <a href=\"https://investor.daktronics.com/static-files/257100da-05a9-46a8-aabb-46a6b94ce736\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">leading position in the US market</a> with a promising outlook</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/183305131/image_183305131.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742308-daktronics-q2-digital-transformation-set-to-drive-strong-margin-growth", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:30:03"}, {"id": "4741491", "title": "2 REITs To Buy Before December 18th", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"clock series\" data-id=\"157394764\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peepo/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Fed has already cut interest rates two times, and it is expected to cut rates again at the next meeting on December 18th.</p> <p></p> <p>This is very bullish for REITs (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VNQ\" title=\"Vanguard Real Estate ETF\">VNQ</a>) because their market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157394764/image_157394764.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741491-2-reits-to-buy-before-december-18th", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:25:00"}, {"id": "4742305", "title": "BNY Mellon Core Plus Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wooden cube block with Value business word and plus icon on blue background. Mission, Vision, and Core Values Concept\" data-id=\"1691340619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Userba011d64_201/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <blockquote><p>\u201cWe expect economic growth in most developed economies to moderate to sub-trend levels, while inflation gradually eases back to target levels. Monetary policy easing is set to continue through the final quarter of the year and into</p></blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691340619/image_1691340619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742305-bny-mellon-core-plus-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:18:00"}, {"id": "4742304", "title": "Roku's Takeover Rumor And How It Impacts Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wealthy Entrepreneur\" data-id=\"157444694\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">RichVintage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Recently, American technology company Roku (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ROKU\" title=\"Roku, Inc.\">ROKU</a></span>) has been the subject of equity research reports by a handful of sell-side equity research firms that have issued multiple reports expecting the San Jose, CA-based streaming device maker to be</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157444694/image_157444694.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742304-rokus-takeover-rumor-and-how-it-impacts-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:15:41"}, {"id": "4742318", "title": "NAV Monitor: U.S. Equity REITs End November At 6.5% Median Discount", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate concept business, home insurance and real estate protection. Real estate investment concept. Buy and sell houses and real estate online on a virtual screen.\" data-id=\"2154752387\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">phakphum patjangkata</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Publicly listed US equity real estate investment trusts closed Nov. 29 at a median 6.5% discount to their consensus net asset value per share estimates, 2.8 percentage points down from a median discount of 9.3% as of Nov. 1, according to S&amp;P Global Market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2154752387/image_2154752387.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742318-nav-monitor-us-equity-reits-end-november-at-6-5-percent-median-discount", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 16:10:00"}, {"id": "4741877", "title": "Rare Stock Picks In November 2024 - From 28 Discerning Analysts", "description": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/3/saupload_needle_in_haystack.png\" vspace=\"6\" hspace=\"6\" alt=\"\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"> </p> <p dir=\"ltr\">November turned out to be yet another buy the dip opportunity. Even with the SPY up ~27%